mixes.name: jungletrain.net promomix may 2021
mixes.comment:
jungletrain.net is proud to present: Watcher - jungletrain.net promomix may 2021

When a DJ is on his sixth installment, writing a splashing introduction becomes a challenge. Then again, Watcher is past the need of needing one. Closing in on 10 years on the train, and much longer in the scene, his tight mixes, controlled pace and refined flows provide a focal point for any party line-up or night of radio programming. This time around, Watcher lets the mix do the talking. We hope you enjoy it! 

Should this mix find you wanting more, Watcher can be heard on jungletrain.net every other Thursday night from 21.00 - 22.30 CEST, 20.00 - 21.30 BST, 15.00 - 16.30 EDT, 12.00 - 13.30 PDT!

Links:
https://www.mixcloud.com/watcher/
https://soundcloud.com/watcher_dnb
https://www.facebook.com/watcherdnb/

mixes.name: jungletrain.net promomix summer 2021
mixes.comment:
jungletrain.net is proud to present: Darkstar - jungletrain.net promomix summer 2021

Your personal breakbeat sherpa this summer is Darkstar, back with his fourth Jungletrain promomix installment. The trailhead for this journey is a deep halftime vibe that touches on some esoteric thinkin' music before launching headfirst into amen-laden jungle.

The subdued choppage provides a vibrant plateau of barely contained energy through the majority of the mix, painting a backdrop of a diverse tapestry that enshrouds the skyline that is our musical home. Concluding the the trek, our path winds down towards a cerebral multidimensional meditation guided by modern production techniques that fertilize the rhythmic soil for future generations to contemplate.

Wrapping up, Darkstar adds: "My favorite moment in the mix has to be Aeon Four's Babylon into Rumbleton's Sound Family. The Maya Angelou 'Still I Rise' quotation fits so perfectly in the spacious dubwise breakdown, with the messages interleaving on multiple levels. Recognize and process the past to improve our collective future. One life, one love. Thanks for listening."

We hope you enjoy this summer's promomix, and if you do, make sure to check out Rinse & Repeat Radio every tuesday night from 17.00 - 19.00 PDT, 20.00 - 22.00 EDT, 01.00 - 03.00 BST, 02.00 - 04.00 CEST!

We're taking a short break this summer, see you back in September for the next promomix! Stay safe and Buddha Bless!

Links:
https://rinseandrepeatradio.com/
https://recondnb.net/

--
